{"data":{"page":{"title":"How to sign & verify messages on Ethereum","slug":"how-to/getting-started/how-to-sign-and-verify-messages-on-ethereum","originalSlug":"how-to/getting-started/how-to-sign-and-verify-messages-on-ethereum","description":"Addresses & Balances","datePublished":"2018-04-18","dateModified":"2018-12-19","parent":{"__typename":"Category","title":"Getting Started"},"breadcrumbs":[{"title":"How-To Guides","slug":"how-to"},{"title":"Getting Started","slug":"how-to/getting-started"},{"title":"How to sign & verify messages on Ethereum","slug":"how-to/getting-started/how-to-sign-and-verify-messages-on-ethereum"}]},"file":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<h3>Why?</h3>\n<p>With Ethereum, signatures are a way of providing evidence that a specific user has access to a specific address.</p>\n<p>For example, if user A wants to provide evidence to user B that user A has access to address X, they could sign a message with their private key, stating that user A has access to address X, then share the signed signature with user B. If the signature is correct, user B can verify that user A has access to address X without user A ever having to share their private key to user B.</p>\n<h3>Signing a message</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>Go to the <a href=\"https://mycrypto.com/sign-and-verify-message/sign\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">message signing page on MyCrypto</a>. Make sure that you see the green \"MyCrypto, Inc\" certificate in your URL bar. <a href=\"/troubleshooting/cannot-see-the-extended-validation-certificate\">Don't see it?</a></li>\n<li>Access your wallet.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/bdf8c2a5d436804362b5e9eb42748605/86cce/accessing-wallet.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 750px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 45.25252525252525%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"accessing wallet\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/bdf8c2a5d436804362b5e9eb42748605/9c5b2/accessing-wallet.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/bdf8c2a5d436804362b5e9eb42748605/b3da4/accessing-wallet.png 188w,\n/static/bdf8c2a5d436804362b5e9eb42748605/3057b/accessing-wallet.png 375w,\n/static/bdf8c2a5d436804362b5e9eb42748605/9c5b2/accessing-wallet.png 750w,\n/static/bdf8c2a5d436804362b5e9eb42748605/86cce/accessing-wallet.png 990w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>Enter the message that you wish to use to prove your ownership of the address.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d1feb8097f00fe5ce9afdecbf9132b87/995f0/signing-message.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 750px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 28.13852813852814%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAAGCAYAAADDl76dAAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAAAZUlEQVQY05WQQQ7AIAgE/f9jAfHgQZGKsbQnSzeZSMBMAinnrF3Ekbvu3ZHXbIxxJDGzmrSU4jAbrESkrTW1fIlcGPk0dfs9Jyx8xAGh/khoZQBctwJExQnNewLA6uHuGbXWkPQCFMDZ0daEAm0AAAAASUVORK5CYII='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"signing message\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/d1feb8097f00fe5ce9afdecbf9132b87/9c5b2/signing-message.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d1feb8097f00fe5ce9afdecbf9132b87/b3da4/signing-message.png 188w,\n/static/d1feb8097f00fe5ce9afdecbf9132b87/3057b/signing-message.png 375w,\n/static/d1feb8097f00fe5ce9afdecbf9132b87/9c5b2/signing-message.png 750w,\n/static/d1feb8097f00fe5ce9afdecbf9132b87/995f0/signing-message.png 924w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>Click the big blue \"Sign Message\" button.</li>\n<li>Your signed message will appear in a box below. It should look a bit like this:</li>\n</ol>\n<pre><code class=\"language-json\">{\n  \"address\": \"0x497D15829C338f9e817314662febC7ccE47E69b1\",\n  \"msg\": \"This is proof that I, user A, have access to this address.\",\n  \"sig\": \"0xfa076d068ca83ec87203f394c630a1a992f0d39eac5e761aec4c90011204f0b776adf698fe3d626dfd4e7c6ef1f89adb4b9831adaeac72dd19093381265b45471b\",\n  \"version\": \"2\"\n}\n</code></pre>\n<p>You can use this message as proof that you own an address, and share it with anyone.</p>\n<h3>Verifying a message</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>Go to the <a href=\"https://mycrypto.com/sign-and-verify-message/verify\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">message verifying page on MyCrypto</a>.</li>\n<li>Enter the signed message that you want to check, and click \"Verify Message.\"</li>\n</ol>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/91da747bcc6a347407367715b5b62d45/3caad/verifying-message.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 750px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 22.86245353159851%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"verifying message\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/91da747bcc6a347407367715b5b62d45/9c5b2/verifying-message.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/91da747bcc6a347407367715b5b62d45/b3da4/verifying-message.png 188w,\n/static/91da747bcc6a347407367715b5b62d45/3057b/verifying-message.png 375w,\n/static/91da747bcc6a347407367715b5b62d45/9c5b2/verifying-message.png 750w,\n/static/91da747bcc6a347407367715b5b62d45/eb8fc/verifying-message.png 1125w,\n/static/91da747bcc6a347407367715b5b62d45/c78db/verifying-message.png 1500w,\n/static/91da747bcc6a347407367715b5b62d45/3caad/verifying-message.png 1614w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p>If the signature is correct, a green bar will be displayed.</p>"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"how-to/getting-started/how-to-sign-and-verify-messages-on-ethereum","file":"how-to/getting-started/how-to-sign-and-verify-messages-on-ethereum.md"}}